Palmer is having a time in her @deltachildren Serta Angel Whispers Dual Sided Baby Crib Mattress 🕊
A few weeks ago we began transitioning Palmer from her bedside bassinet to her crib for bedtime. She’s been able to roll over to her tummy since before being three months old, so it was time. I, of course 😬 - brought an extra mattress of my own into her room to sleep in until she can fully roll back and forth on her own. Something that eases my mind is that Palmer’s mattress is firm but gentle at the same time. 

All Delta Children products are non-toxic and free from heavy metals. And on top of that, Delta Children donates 10% of all profits to the Safe Sleep Campaign. This mattress may be found at Amazon, Target, & Walmart! They have tons of baby and toddler products, head to @deltachildren and have a look for yourself!

Come with me to get lip filler by one of the best in Ottawa, Ontario - Canada! @sandracarrillo_rio & @refinedimageottawa 💋 
Being an aesthetic injector, doctoral student, and aesthetic trainer — I’m extremely picky with who I choose for my treatments. Many people ask me who I recommend in Ottawa, as I used to be a provider there myself. I always recommend @refinedimageottawa. They have an amazing team & they just moved to a prime location in Westboro! Fun fact, @sandracarrillo_rio almost opened a clinic together in Ottawa then I decided to move back to the US. She is booming now! I missed that train! I’m so proud of all that she has accomplished and I love to watch her grow! 💕
